Willie WILLIAMS, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D17-3073 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. October 11, 2017

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:
